&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;A Little About the Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Demand Generation Specialist at Procare Solutions, you&#39;ll be a key executor in our Growth Marketing team — building and running the campaigns, nurture programs, and reporting workflows that power our pipeline. You&#39;re someone who thrives on getting campaigns out the door cleanly and loves seeing the data come back. You&#39;ll work closely with the Senior Manager of Demand Generation and collaborate across Content, Product Marketing, and Sales.&lt;/p&gt;
