&lt;li&gt;Own campaign QA — reviewing emails, landing pages, and workflows before launch to&amp;nbsp;ensure accuracy and on-brand execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nurture &amp;amp; Automation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and manage multi-touch email nurture programs in Pardot and HubSpot, segmented by persona, lifecycle stage, and product interest&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain list health, manage segmentation, and support lead scoring updates in partnership with Marketing Ops&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously test and optimize nurture programs — monitoring open rates, click-through, and MQL conversion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Analytics &amp;amp; Reporting&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
